@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
title Producing and diffusing a block

|Elected pool|
start
:won the VRF lottery for this slot;
:select transactions from the mempool;
:assemble the block body;
:sign the header with the KES key
(forward-secure);
:attach the VRF proof of election;
:publish the block to peers;

|Network|
:block diffuses to other nodes
(target ~5 seconds);

|Every receiving node|
:verify the VRF proof (legitimate leader?);
:verify the KES signature;
:validate every transaction;
if (all checks pass?) then (yes)
  :append block; extend the chain;
else (no)
  :reject the block;
endif
:apply chain-selection rule
(longest chain; Praos tie-break by VRF);
stop
@enduml
